{"type": "article", "id": 25647, "title": "可以调整温度的桌子", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-19T07:12:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702120304KFma7Dc2SdW5BCbh.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这张餐桌隐藏了电路系统，可以调整桌面特定区域的温度，让准备食材、加热到吃饭都在一张桌子上。它使用了一种 SapienStone 的陶瓷材料，让桌子的厚度只有 6 毫米，从侧面看，餐具就像悬浮在半空中了，简约现代。设计者来自团队 Kram/Weisshaar ，产品刚刚在米兰设计周上展出。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120302AClxgn2jqIyYpcmb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120302u9VDjaFYtZ28Plw0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021203038BJPlM0WFNKQvw4X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120303KlHumaJWqP8nM41t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120304mfXRExkhi9Zl1K7O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}